				<div class="row">
					
					<div class="affari-table">

						<div class="cell">
							
							<div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-2">

															<h2 class="hl1" >Game developers have a voice.</h2>
							
															<p  >The International Game Developers Association (IGDA) is the world’s largest nonprofit membership organization serving all individuals who create games. <br />
<br />
We advance the careers and enhance the lives of game developers by connecting members with their peers, promoting professional development, and advocating for the interests of game developers worldwide.</p>
							
															<a href="https://igda.org/membership/" class="bttn sml "  style="background-color: #64cbd0;" >JOIN THE IGDA TODAY!</a>
							
							</div>

						</div>

					</div>

				</div>

			</div>
		</section>
	
